1.what is data type?
Data type is used give what kind of data is...

There are two types of data....
	1. Primitive data types..
	2.Non primitive data type..
	
	
2.What is primitive data type?
A primitive data type is a fixed in size.
like..byte, short,int, double, long,float, char,boolean..these all have a fixed size...
	
	Created one class called Datatype from there you can refere how to datatypes are working..
	

3. Non primitive data type:-
It does not have a fixed size.
It is also known as reference typeps..
These all are created by programmer ...its not a pre-defined data type.

such as :-
Array
String
Interface
Classes	